{"tid":1215190,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"親身到現場，用自己隻眼睇清楚，自己決定係好重要","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T05:13:57.000Z","uid":203889,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a20b740fca2ec000852e89544dcecd17db65fcb","tid":1215190,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:21:41.000Z","msg":"呢幾日發左好幾個夢<br />\n<br />\n夢入面我上網<br />\n係網上見到d人話<br />\n某地方少人，最好散水<br />\n去到見到既又係另一回事<br />\n根本仲好多人，好需要支援<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係最前面<br />\n中後方都好需要有人站場<br />\n一方面俾壓力對家<br />\n另一方面可以守住多d陣地<br />\n<br />\n係夢入面，網上三毛多就一定，假消息亦一定有<br />\n但其實叫人走既部分亦係普通人<br />\n我明白佢地出於好心，怕人送死<br />\n但我認為大家<strong>既然唔要大台，就要承擔自己做判斷既責任</strong><br />\n唔好因為其他人一兩句說話就跟左人地既想法做野，難聽d講句，咁樣人云亦云仲衰過有大台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夢到呢度我就醒左啦"},{"pid":"5dab2c4b822ef05473447c05433f5234e945a59d","tid":1215190,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"此致<br />\n係夢入面見到既膽小鬼"},{"pid":"a834f384cb897801503961bf183b58e947ef5a3e","tid":1215190,"uid":149844,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"站出嚟睇清楚好重要<br />\nbtw<br />\n呼籲各大市民即日開始行街見到警犬就噓佢<br />\n屌多兩句老母都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc09d947ff752f89d9daca1f5a77163c62425d3","tid":1215190,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:44:29.000Z","msg":"歡迎分享大家既夢境"},{"pid":"971ced61e6236304ca74aba1989ba66f6506f57b","tid":1215190,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"be5673d6ef081724fbf2dd8ee2d63c0e9ae68a52","tid":1215190,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:37:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72cc0312f858417aff2abdb0f8de12a0ae18ef89","tid":1215190,"uid":241676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:4